library(ggplot2)
## Warning: package 'ggplot2' was built under R version 3.5.3
library(dplyr)
## Warning: package 'dplyr' was built under R version 3.5.3
## 
## Attaching package: 'dplyr'

dat <- read.csv("C:/Users/ejjun/Desktop/UC Berkeley Subjects/Fifth Semester/Stat 133/Labs/lab04/data/nba2018-players.csv", colClasses = c("character", "factor", "factor", "integer", "integer", "integer", "integer", "character", "real", "real", "real", "real", "real", "real", "real"))
# scatterplot (option 1)
ggplot(data = dat) +
  geom_point(aes(x = points, y = salary))

# scatterplot (option 2)
ggplot(data = dat, aes(x = points, y = salary)) +
  geom_point()

# GSW
ggplot(data = filter(dat, team == 'GSW'), aes(x = height, y = weight)) + geom_point()

# using geom_text
ggplot(data = filter(dat, team == 'GSW'), aes(x = height, y = weight, label = player)) + geom_point() + geom_text()

# using geom_label
ggplot(data = filter(dat, team == 'GSW'), aes(x = height, y = weight, label = player)) + geom_point() + geom_label()

# geom_text labels the points but using a text overlay that keeps the points visible. geom_label labels the text with a textbox like label replacing the points completely.
# density plot
ggplot(data = dat, aes(x = salary)) + geom_density()

# histogram binwidth 50
ggplot(data = dat, aes(x = points2)) + geom_histogram(binwidth = 50, boundary = 0)

# barchart of position frequencies
ggplot(data = dat, aes(x = position)) + geom_bar()

# scatterplot of exp and salary of centers with regression line
ggplot(data = filter(dat, position == 'C'), aes(x = experience, y = salary)) + geom_point() + geom_smooth(method = lm)

# scatterplot of exp and salary of centers with loess line
ggplot(data = filter(dat, position == 'C'), aes(x = experience, y = salary)) + geom_point() + geom_smooth(method = loess)

# scatterplot of exp and salary with position facet
ggplot(data = dat, aes(x = experience, y = salary)) + geom_point() + facet_wrap(~ position)

# scatterplot of exp and salary with team facet
ggplot(data = dat, aes(x = experience, y = salary)) + geom_point() + facet_wrap(~ team)

# density plot of age with team facet
ggplot(data = dat, aes(x = age)) + geom_density() + facet_wrap(~ team)

# scatterplot of height and weight with position facet
ggplot(data = dat, aes(x = height, y = weight)) + geom_point() + facet_wrap(~ position)

# scatterplot of height and weight with position facet and 2d density
ggplot(data = dat, aes(x = height, y = weight)) + geom_point() + geom_density2d() + facet_wrap(~ position)

# scatterplot of exp and salary of Warriors with position facet
ggplot(data = filter(dat, team == 'GSW'), aes(x = experience, y = salary)) + geom_point() + theme_bw()

# scatterplot of height and weight with position facet and different theme
ggplot(data = dat, aes(x = height, y = weight)) + geom_point() + facet_wrap(~ position) + theme_minimal()
